        <span>{{imgsCount}}/4</span>
      </div>
      <div class="wc-car-check__tips">
        请按以下示意图拍摄车辆外观照片（必选）
      </div>
      <div class="wc-car-check__line">
        <div class="wc-car-check__line__item"
             v-xy-moving-btn>
          <i class="icons-car-return-front-left-2-outer">
            <div class="icons-car icons-car-return-front-left-2-inner"
